### Context

The dataset contains data from residential (single-family) homes in wake county, NC, from the 1800s to July 2021. This data has been processed to contain only single-family residential records and variables directly related to property sales.

### Content

The Wake County Housing dataset contains 15 explanatory variables which can be used to predict the property selling price.


### Acknowledgements

 The original data was accessed 07/20/2021 from the wake county [website](https://www.wakegov.com/departments-government/tax-administration/data-files-statistics-and-reports/real-estate-property-data-files).


### Inspiration

Predict housing Price in Wake County, NC
